# Portfolio Website — Full-Stack Project with Free Hosting Guide

Welcome to my personal **Portfolio Website**, a creative and fully responsive full-stack project built using **HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap**, **PHP**, and **MySQL**. This site is designed to showcase my skills, projects, and online presence with a unique visual experience inspired by modern website previews — but with a twist of my own!

---

## 🚀 Live Preview

*This project is a work in progress.* The final version will be updated soon. Currently, the site uses a template layout generated with the help of AI prompts, designed to reflect my vision and bring my ideas to life.

Check out the live version here: 🔗 [Portfolio on Vercel](#) *(update link)*

---

## ✨ Features

* ✅ Fully responsive and mobile-friendly design
* 🎨 Unique and modern UI inspired by various web designs
* 🌐 Built using:

  * HTML5
  * CSS3
  * JavaScript (Vanilla)
  * Bootstrap 5
* 🔌 Integrated with:

  * Font Awesome for icons
  * Google Fonts for elegant typography
  * Free Public APIs for dynamic content
* Backend:

  * PHP for handling forms and dynamic content
  * MySQL database for storing contact messages, projects, etc.
* ☁️ Hosted on Vercel (frontend) and free PHP+MySQL hosts (backend)
* 💾 Code versioned and managed using GitHub

